],{"class":94},[88,1247,1248],{"class":97}," -v",[88,1250,1251],{"class":101}," https:\u002F\u002Fgoogle.com\n",[12,1253,1254],{},[15,1255],{"alt":1229,"src":1256},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fother\u002Fcurl\u002F20250514222800.png",[12,1258,1259,1261,1262,1265],{},[27,1260,1235],{}," 除了顯示 ",[27,1263,1264],{},"request\u002Fresponse"," 之外，還會顯示 DNS、TCP 握手、TLS 握手等過程，這些都是有助於 Debug 的（內容太多所以可以自己試試看）。",[20,1267,1268],{"id":1268},"將回應內容寫入檔案",[12,1270,1271,1272,1275],{},"如果回傳的內容比較多時，你可以使用 ",[27,1273,1274],{},"-o"," 將回應的內容寫入檔案，這邊我們就這樣寫：",[79,1277,1279],{"className":81,"code":1278,"language":83,"meta":84,"style":84},"curl -o google.html https:\u002F\u002Fgoogle.com\n",[27,1280,1281],{"__ignoreMap":84},[88,1282,1283,1285,1288,1291],{"class":90,"line":91},[88,1284,17],{"class":94},[88,1286,1287],{"class":97}," -o",[88,1289,1290],{"class":101}," google.html",[88,1292,1251],{"class":101},[12,1294,1295,1297,1298,1301],{},[27,1296,1274],{}," 參數後面接著你要寫入的檔案名稱，這邊我們就將回應的內容寫入 ",[27,1299,1300],{},"google.html"," 檔案裡面，這樣就可以將回應的內容寫入檔案了。",[20,1303,1305],{"id":1304},"指定-user-agent","指定 User-Agent",[12,1307,1308,1309,1312],{},"那麼可不可以指定 User-Agent（告訴 Server 我是誰、我使用什麼瀏覽器）呢？當然可以，這邊我們可以使用 ",[27,1310,1311],{},"-A"," 參數來指定 User-Agent，這邊我們就這樣寫：",[79,1314,1316],{"className":81,"code":1315,"language":83,"meta":84,"style":84},"curl -A \"Mozilla\u002F5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit\u002F537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome\u002F58.0.3029.110 Safari\u002F537.3\" https:\u002F\u002Fgoogle.com\n",[27,1317,1318],{"__ignoreMap":84},[88,1319,1320,1322,1325,1328],{"class":90,"line":91},[88,1321,17],{"class":94},[88,1323,1324],{"class":97}," -A",[88,1326,1327],{"class":101}," \"Mozilla\u002F5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit\u002F537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome\u002F58.0.3029.110 Safari\u002F537.3\"",[88,1329,1251],{"class":101},[12,1331,252,1332,1334],{},[27,1333,1311],{}," 參數後面接著你要指定的 User-Agent，這樣就可以指定 User-Agent 了。",[12,1336,1337,1338,1340],{},"為什麼會特別提到 "